---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="DMCA Policy - How I Claude Code" description="DMCA takedown policy for How I Claude Code - report copyright infringement.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">DMCA Takedown Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Reporting Copyright Infringement</h2>
        <p>
          How I Claude Code respects intellectual property rights. If you believe content on How I Claude Code infringes your copyright, please send a DMCA takedown notice to:
        </p>
        <p class="font-mono bg-muted p-4 rounded">
          dmca@howi.cc
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Required Information</h2>
        <p>Your notice must include:</p>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Your contact information</strong>: Name, address, phone, email</li>
          <li><strong>Description of copyrighted work</strong>: What work is being infringed</li>
          <li><strong>Location of infringing content</strong>: URL(s) of the content on How I Claude Code</li>
          <li><strong>Good faith statement</strong>: You believe the use is not authorized</li>
          <li><strong>Accuracy statement</strong>: Information is accurate, under penalty of perjury</li>
          <li><strong>Signature</strong>: Physical or electronic signature of copyright owner or agent</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Counter-Notification</h2>
        <p>
          If you believe your content was removed in error, you may file a counter-notification. Include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your contact information</li>
          <li>Description of removed content and its location</li>
          <li>Statement under penalty of perjury that removal was mistaken</li>
          <li>Consent to jurisdiction in your location</li>
          <li>Your signature</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Repeat Infringers</h2>
        <p>
          We will terminate accounts of users who are repeat copyright infringers in appropriate circumstances.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Send DMCA notices to: <a href="mailto:dmca@howi.cc">dmca@howi.cc</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
